dcterms:description: The CATCH dataset consists of 350 whole-slide images (WSIs) with annotations covering six non-neoplastic tissues and seven tumor classes, used for training and evaluating patch-level multi-class classification methods.
dcterms:title: CAnine CuTaneous Cancer Histology (CATCH)

dcterms:description: P-CATCH is a new benchmark dataset derived from the CATCH dataset, specifically curated for evaluating patch-level multi-class classification methods in whole-slide images.
dcterms:title: P-CATCH
